                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5813" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1477</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8021 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国外订单锐减怎么办？且看众普森立足国内大循环的探索之旅</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">How should We Do if Foreign Orders Plummet?Look at an Exploration Tour of Zopoise’ Stategic Adjustment Based on the Domestic Cycle</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">伍喆，何小金，张婉清，王轩，文子琪</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湘潭大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">众普森科技(株洲)有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">能源工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">众普森；外向型企业；LED照明行业；战略伙伴；国内大循环</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Zopoise; export-oriented enterprises; LED lighting industry; strategic partner; great domestic cycle</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">众普森科技(株洲)有限公司是一家主要生产LED灯的出口企业，其生产的泛光灯、投光灯出口量连续几年全国排名第一。众普森产品有90%出口海外，只有10%左右面向国内市场，在新冠疫情冲击下出口量陡然下降，而且在全球疫情尚未完成控制等诸多不确定情形下，过去倚重的海外市场能否“存活”还是个很大的未知数。此情此景，众普森何去何从？本案例描述了该公司的一系列“自救运动”，探究在面临“生死”考验之际，企业如何从主要依赖出口的外向型业务向立足国内大循环进行转型的过程，展示了企业在战略调整、资源协同、业务转型、逆境生长的奋斗历程，展示了皮远军总经理等企业领导的战略决策能力和独特的领导魅力。案例旨在帮助工商企业管理专业学生学习如何在外部环境发生重大变化时的决策流程和方法，学习并理解战略合作伙伴选择之于市场开拓的意义。至目前为止，这是一个积极拥抱并成功转型国内市场的经典案例，是实践“构建以国内大循环为主体、国内国际双循环相互促进的新发展格局”的精彩样本。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Zopoise Technology (Zhuzhou) Co., Ltd. (hereinafter referred to as &quot;Zopoise&quot;) is a major manufacturer of LED lights export enterprises, with floodlights and spotlights’ export volume ranking first for several years. 90% of its products are exported overseas, only about 10 percent to the domestic market. Under the impact of COVID-19, Zopoise faces difficulties in developing domestic markets as well as saving overseas markets, which have seen a sharp drop in orders. This case, by describing a series of &quot;Self-help Actions&quot; of Zopoise, explores how such an export-oriented enterprise transforms itself on the domestic cycle by strategic adjustment, resource coordination, business transformation and growth under adverse circumstances and it shows the strategic decision-making ability and unique leadership charm of the general manager of Pi Yuanjun. The purpose of the case study is to help students learn how to make decisions when the external environment changes significantly, and to understand the significance of strategic partner selection So far, this is a classic case as well as a wonderful sample of the construction practice of “the domestic big cycle as the main, domestic and international double-cycle mutual promotion of the new development pattern.”</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">战略变革管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-12</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
